{"tid":2365980,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[時窮節乃現] 黑人民主黨喬治亞州州議員轉投共和黨：我要阻止社會主義入侵","createTime":"2021-01-14T07:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T05:28:58.000Z","uid":276356,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"977b712f49d405c3b15fd82f4e4e3921b355f535","tid":2365980,"uid":276356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepVernonJones/status/1347670329242624004?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepVernonJones%2Fstatus%2F1347670329242624004%3Fs%3D19&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=356440a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepVernonJones%2Fstatus%2F1347670329242624004%3Fs%3D19&h=6f22c73a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepVernonJones/status/1347670329242624004?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/1/6/n12671532.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F1%2F6%2Fn12671532.htm&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=50d8f15f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/1/6/n12671532.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2021年01月07日訊】（大紀元記者顏殊璟綜合報導）週三（6日），美國喬治亞州民主黨州眾議員、川普總統的支持者弗農&middot;瓊斯（Vernon Jones）宣布，他正在轉為共和黨籍。<br />\n<br />\n瓊斯表示，他將加入共和黨。<br />\n<br />\n「共和黨現在比以往任何時候都更急需懂得如何戰鬥的領導人。我懂得該如何戰鬥。」瓊斯在一份聲明中說。<br />\n<br />\n現年60歲的瓊斯，自2017年以來擔任州眾議員。1993年至2001年，他也曾擔任過州眾議員。<br />\n<br />\n瓊斯去年宣布支持川普總統。最近幾週，他還為共和黨候選人助選，其中包括喬州參議員凱利‧洛夫勒（Kelly Loeffler）和大衛&middot;珀杜（David Perdue）。<br />\n<br />\n上週末，瓊斯接受新唐人英文節目「The Nation Speaks」採訪時表示，他正在支持共和黨人阻止社會主義滲入喬州社區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「更重要的是，當你看看喬州的現狀，（就知道）喬州會去往何處，這個國家會去往何處。我們必須守住陣腳，必須確保華盛頓的力量平衡，這樣我們才能繼續阻止左派將我們帶下這個懸崖。」他說。<br />\n<br />\n「我畢生都是民主黨人，但就那兩位民主黨候選人所倡導的而言，我就是不喜歡他們。他們支持社會主義，支持削減警費（Defund Police）。他們不希望（讓學生）擇校。他們希望孩子們繼續困在民主黨政策所造成的失敗學校裡。」他補充說，「我可以這麼說，不是我離棄民主黨，是這個黨離棄了我。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瓊斯近來提出要在2022年競選喬州州務卿。川普和一些共和黨人一直批評喬州共和黨籍州務卿拉芬斯珀格（Brad Raffensperger）對選舉的處理。而拉芬斯珀格似乎在喬州參議院決選前夕洩漏了他與川普的通話。<br />\n<br />\n瓊斯對新唐人表示：「我可以說，我們的州務卿做得很差。」他補充說，拉芬斯珀格與民主黨的同意令「創造了這種缺乏信任和不透明的環境」。<br />\n<br />\n瓊斯拒絕透露自己是否會競選州務卿職位。<br />\n<br />\n拉芬斯珀格及其辦公室則為喬州進行的選舉進行辯護。<br />\n<br />\n（大紀元記者Zachary Stieber對本文作出了貢獻）<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：李緣#"},{"pid":"153be712b3a6de800289dfcf32b5f1968c0a08af","tid":2365980,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你不配做黑人"},{"pid":"fae8124a67c4935138aa6c4f385c81280d12db07","tid":2365980,"uid":310700,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"You ain't black<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfbfb07fe5ffb44d7aa0e80309906a86ce746b4","tid":2365980,"uid":83609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"真時窮節乃現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d43a9a904c0ae47bcd7da2b47d12ef2859deea","tid":2365980,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0285ee8ca34946e4d38e22081799adae7673ba7e","tid":2365980,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"當民主黨不再民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8553f132415a7ec15842709eb48313b9c88be1d","tid":2365980,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.